abstract: >-
  A one-stop curated hub of free resources, tools, courses, cheat sheets and
  best practices for developers, students, professors and academics, and
  scientists and researchers — with a flagship 2026 AI and Agents section
  covering the Model Context Protocol, agent frameworks, coding agents,
  retrieval-augmented generation, evaluation and observability, and
  open-model inference and fine-tuning.
